Thursday, February 16, 1995

MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

93-1384. No. CA-9123. Musisca v. Massillon Community Hosp. Stark County,

This cause is pending before the court as a discretionary appeal. On December 20, 1994, this court ordered appellants to show cause by January 9,1995, why this cause should not be dismissed. Appellants filed no response to the order to show cause. Upon consideration thereof,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed, effective February 14, 1995.
